    "category": "devops",
    "description": "為 Streamlit / Web Dashboard 設定定時開關排程，使用 no_agent=True 純腳本運行，零 token 消耗",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "author": "Hermes Community",
    "license": "MIT",
    "platforms": [],
